title: #62: LA Story (Cort McCown, Steve Rannazzisi, Ari Shaffir)
itunes:title: LA Story with Cort McCown and Steve Rannazzisi
description: Cort McCown invited Steve Rannazzisi and me to his apartment to talk about his old days as a Hollywood heartthrob. He had some crazy times when he was younger. He boned women I could only dream of. And a few of them that I actually did dream of.
